folder: Columbia Heights & Cranberry Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
82-84 Columbia Heights, west side, opposite Cranberry Street (seen in the foreground). This is a set of two views. No. 2 shows the Borough Hall section of Brooklyn in the background.

April 4, 1932.
View 2: April 5, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Brooklyn: Columbia Heights - Cranberry Street
